# User Stories

### Must Have

#### User Story 1

As a first-time investor, I want to compare a few simple investment options, so that I can understand which option may suit me without needing prior investment knowledge.

Priority: Must

---

#### User Story 2

As a first-time investor, I want to clearly see both potential gains and potential losses, so that I can make an informed investment decision.

Priority: Must

---

#### User Story 3

As a first-time investor, I want investment terms explained in simple language, so that I do not feel confused by financial terminology.

Priority: Must

---

#### User Story 4

As a first-time investor, I want to explore investment outcomes using mock money, so that I can learn without risking real money.

Priority: Must

---

### Should Have

#### User Story 5

As a first-time investor, I want to understand how long I may need to keep my money invested, so that I can set realistic expectations before investing.

Priority: Should

---

### Could Have

#### User Story 6

As a first-time investor, I want to compare different investment scenarios, so that I can better understand how risk affects returns.

Priority: Could

---

#### User Story 7

As a first-time investor, I want to reflect on my comfort level after viewing possible outcomes, so that I can decide whether I am ready to start investing.

Priority: Could
